sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { Box, Container, Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material'; import { styled } from '@mui/system'; import logo from "../assets/images/ibrahim.png"; import ibrahim from "../assets/images/ibrahim.png"; import ahmad from "../assets/images/ahmad.png"; import '../css/contactUs.css'; const DoctorCard = styled(Grid)(({ theme }) => ({ background: theme.palette.background.paper, borderRadius: 12, boxShadow: '0px 0px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)', padding: theme.spacing(3), textAlign: 'center', })); const Doctors = () => { return ( <> Our Doctors Meet our experienced and qualified doctors who are here to help you with your healthcare needs. Dr. Ibrahim Dr. Ibrahim is an experienced and highly skilled physician with over 10 years of experience. He specializes in internal medicine and has a passion for providing personalized care to his patients. Dr. Ahmad Dr. Ahmad is a board-certified family physician with over 15 years of experience. He is passionate about providing comprehensive care to his patients and believes in building lasting relationships with them. ); }; export default Doctors;
